title: Mike Hartsfield from New Age Records/Outspoken
itunes:title: Mike Hartsfield from New Age Records/Outspoken
description:
Mike Hartsfield is the owner of New Age Records (Unbroken, 1134, Spawn, Strife) and played the guitar for Outspoken. We caught up at his screen printing shop a few weeks ago and discussed bad business practices, zine culture and independent wrestling. Brought to you in conjunction with Propertyofzack.com
